{"tid":2194902,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港最後防線：保育廣東話","createTime":"2020-09-08T22:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T06:25:27.000Z","uid":52779,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8efe5b214faed8b7f5ee0807aca68755ccea88ce","tid":2194902,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T22:03:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/266GGMmzMrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F266GGMmzMrg&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=02b92a3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/266GGMmzMrg</a><br />\n<br />\n引文：<br />\n隨著香港面目全非，如何保全香港文化，同樣寸土必爭。究竟廣東話文化代表香港的歷史如何開始？未來會否逐漸失去這特色？歐陽偉豪博士 (Ben Sir) 一直努力推廣廣東話文化，認為這是香港人的最後防線，也喜見近年社會開始接受廣東話書寫，連政府官方社交媒體也仿效，證明大勢不可逆轉，不要輕言放棄。<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=6781a2f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=fc204759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...</a><br />\nPatreon: <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/simonshen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsimonshen&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=2655b603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/simonshen</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsimonshen_glos&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=28aee41e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"htt